values: Some of you guys already figured it out, but i have a new journal _unheart. Added only 12 people from this journal, mainly because i'm still interested in reading their journals, or they comment and give me advice. I already have enough friends on my list. I'm not adding anyone else, unless i ask them first. Check back here another time.
